1
00:00:00,653 --> 00:00:03,532
&lt;-IM&gt; BAREAYON BEKASETA MISPAR SHTAYIM.

2
00:00:02,627 --> 00:00:04,359
KEN, TODA RABA.

3
00:00:03,555 --> 00:00:05,523
ANA, HAMSHIKHI ET SIPUREKH.

4
00:00:05,293 --> 00:00:06,384
BEVAKASHA.

5
00:00:07,116 --> 00:00:10,502
AZ, BEDEREKH, oyfn veg geyendik

6
00:00:11,233 --> 00:00:17,100
iz, hot men nisht, zikh geto-, tomer hobn d- di bafelkerung hobn gevolt,

7
00:00:17,100 --> 00:00:22,013
s'iz geven &lt;m-&gt; mentshn, vos zey hobn yo gevolt varfn undz a shtikl broyt oder vos,

8
00:00:22,013 --> 00:00:24,865
un az m'hot gezen, hot men zey geshosn,

9
00:00:24,865 --> 00:00:26,617
oder hot men zey &lt;azoy&gt;...

10
00:00:26,617 --> 00:00:30,059
hobn zey shoyn moyre gehat dos tsu tun. zey hobn gevust, zey torn nisht.

11
00:00:30,133 --> 00:00:31,713
mitn veg geyendik,

12
00:00:32,006 --> 00:00:36,784
hobn a sakh mentshn vos ikh hob bagegnt, vos s'iz, biz hayntikn tog

13
00:00:36,784 --> 00:00:38,255
ken ikh nisht fargesn,

14
00:00:38,255 --> 00:00:41,299
vi eltern hobn avekgevorfn kleyne kinder

15
00:00:41,389 --> 00:00:43,387
mit a shmate oyfn veg.

16
00:00:44,005 --> 00:00:48,398
un zey zenen geven... un az mir hobn gevolt zikh onbeygn, zey gebn a shtikl broyt...

17
00:00:48,398 --> 00:00:54,242
m'hot zey nisht gevolt shisn. zey hobn gevolt, di daytshn, az zey zoln dortn oysgeyn on esn.

18
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:57,971
un az mir zenen durkhgegangen un mir hobn dos gezen, mayn tate un ikh,

19
00:00:58,028 --> 00:00:59,476
un er hot gevolt

20
00:00:59,476 --> 00:01:02,547
nemen a shtikl broyt un aroyfleygn oyf der shmate...

21
00:01:02,547 --> 00:01:04,519
dray kinder zenen geven...

22
00:01:04,812 --> 00:01:09,028
hot, hot er bakumen, di, petsh ibern kop mit der nagayke.

23
00:01:09,975 --> 00:01:15,337
vos ge- un dos iz ge- vil ikh aykh zogn, m'hot nisht, keyner nisht getort undz helfn.

24
00:01:16,388 --> 00:01:20,162
mir zenen ongekumen keyn OBODIVKA, hob ikh aykh dertseylt.

25
00:01:20,337 --> 00:01:23,959
zenen mir gegangen vayter. mir zenen vayter gegangen,

26
00:01:24,741 --> 00:01:28,053
 Bershad, dos heyst, VINNITSKAYA OBLAST'.

27
00:01:28,386 --> 00:01:30,168
iz geven a geto,

28
00:01:30,478 --> 00:01:32,598
a groys geto in Bershad,

29
00:01:33,516 --> 00:01:36,109
nor undz hot men nisht gelozt in geto.

30
00:01:36,655 --> 00:01:38,674
m'hot undz getribn vayter

31
00:01:39,473 --> 00:01:42,684
in a farmakhtn lager. dos heyst kolkhoz,

32
00:01:42,684 --> 00:01:44,107
ABER dos iz a lager.

33
00:01:44,316 --> 00:01:46,352
dort hot keyner nisht getort...

34
00:01:46,476 --> 00:01:48,261
keyn mentshn iz nisht geven.

35
00:01:48,261 --> 00:01:50,033
oyfn frayen feld.

36
00:01:50,033 --> 00:01:51,923
dray, &lt;, s-&gt;

37
00:01:51,923 --> 00:01:54,858
dortn zenen geven khaze-, khazeyrim hobn gelebt.

38
00:01:54,858 --> 00:01:58,011
hot men undz arayngevorfn azoy, oyf dr'erd.

39
00:01:58,011 --> 00:01:59,126
vinter.

40
00:01:59,149 --> 00:02:01,424
yeder a kleyn pitsl plats.

41
00:02:01,424 --> 00:02:04,374
fun toyznt finef hundert mentshn zenen mir geven.

42
00:02:06,051 --> 00:02:08,340
toyznt finef hundert mentshn.

43
00:02:08,937 --> 00:02:10,420
yede nakht,

44
00:02:10,420 --> 00:02:11,627
yedn tog,

45
00:02:11,805 --> 00:02:14,561
veyniker un veyniker. m'iz oysgeshtorbn

46
00:02:14,561 --> 00:02:16,848
fun kelt, fun hunger,

47
00:02:16,848 --> 00:02:17,959
fun tif,

48
00:02:18,403 --> 00:02:20,889
vayl vifl, fun layz,

49
00:02:20,889 --> 00:02:22,459
di layz hobn gekrokhn.

50
00:02:22,459 --> 00:02:25,738
nisht bodn, nisht, gornisht.

51
00:02:25,828 --> 00:02:31,620
un ver s'iz geshtorbn, un ver m'hot derharget. den ershtn vinter iz geven CHRISTMAS. dos ge-

52
00:02:31,620 --> 00:02:34,203
hot men &lt;undz ara-&gt;, den e- den ershtn moment

53
00:02:34,203 --> 00:02:37,871
vos hot undz getrofn, hot men derharget mayn tate. zenen arayngekumen,

54
00:02:37,877 --> 00:02:40,368
 &lt;a&gt; ge- a kozak,

55
00:02:40,493 --> 00:02:44,674
di farkoyfte, &lt;es&gt; zenen geven farkoyfte rusishe dort&lt;e&gt;,

56
00:02:44,674 --> 00:02:45,633
kozakn.

57
00:02:45,943 --> 00:02:50,105
zey hobn im gebrakht, zey hobn gebrakht dem daytsh mit di rumener ahin tsu.

58
00:02:50,179 --> 00:02:53,618
zey hobn gebrakht, zey hobn gezogt, "do iz der lager fun yidn.

59
00:02:53,618 --> 00:02:56,839
kum, lomir haynt, zikh nekome nemen."

60
00:02:57,182 --> 00:03:00,116
zenen zey arayngekumen un vemen zey hobn

61
00:03:00,116 --> 00:03:03,441
gekent hobn zey... zey hobn a sakh mentshn derharget un dem,

62
00:03:03,441 --> 00:03:05,900
un di mentshn, dos ershte iz geven mayn tate,

63
00:03:06,227 --> 00:03:08,038
un mayn feter,

64
00:03:08,038 --> 00:03:09,950
vos hot geheysn Leyb

65
00:03:09,990 --> 00:03:11,182
&lt;BRECHER&gt;...

66
00:03:11,256 --> 00:03:13,123
ir hot dort farshribn...

67
00:03:13,399 --> 00:03:17,224
er iz nokh dray teg geshtorbn, nokh, nokh mayn tate,

68
00:03:17,224 --> 00:03:17,969
fun di

69
00:03:17,969 --> 00:03:21,133
petsh un fun di, vos m'hot im azoy,

70
00:03:21,133 --> 00:03:24,356
iz er dray teg nokh mayn tate geshtorbn.

71
00:03:25,161 --> 00:03:27,095
di geshtorbene mentshn

72
00:03:27,203 --> 00:03:28,935
hot men nisht bagrobn.

73
00:03:29,245 --> 00:03:31,838
m'hot zey &lt;ara-&gt; m'hot zey geleygt in vinkl.

74
00:03:32,282 --> 00:03:35,381
iz dem gantsn vinter zenen mir geven mit di toyte,

75
00:03:35,674 --> 00:03:37,996
zey in vinkl un mir lebn zey,

76
00:03:39,336 --> 00:03:41,524
vayl s'iz nisht geven dortn,

77
00:03:42,357 --> 00:03:43,961
vos m'hot gelebt.

78
00:03:43,961 --> 00:03:48,139
zey hot UNK, zey hobn arayngevorfn, me zol dort, oysgeyn

79
00:03:48,297 --> 00:03:50,181
far hunger, far kelt,

80
00:03:50,254 --> 00:03:51,952
far alemen.

81
00:03:52,414 --> 00:03:54,945
vi hot geheysn dos plats, der kolkhoz?

82
00:03:53,528 --> 00:03:54,838
FLORINO.

83
00:03:59,181 --> 00:04:02,333
un s'- &lt;m- m-&gt; biz tsun friling

84
00:04:02,944 --> 00:04:04,558
zenen mir geblibn

85
00:04:05,290 --> 00:04:09,674
tsvontsik mentshn, fuftsn mentshn, UNK, genoy ken ikh nisht visn,

86
00:04:09,674 --> 00:04:13,737
nor ale zenen oysgeshtorbn un di toyte zenen geven mit undz.

87
00:04:13,795 --> 00:04:16,280
di &lt;g- g- di ge-&gt; shtsheres

88
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:17,685
mit di mayz

89
00:04:17,793 --> 00:04:22,005
hobn gekrokhn oyf undz, un der shney iz gelegn oyf undz.

90
00:04:22,401 --> 00:04:25,983
un va- nisht vashn, nisht esn, nisht trinken.

91
00:04:25,983 --> 00:04:28,945
azoy hobn mir oysgehaltn biz friling.

92
00:04:29,573 --> 00:04:35,476
vos iz geven, ge- der, der gl- der g- vos mir hobn oysgehaltn biz friling,

93
00:04:35,476 --> 00:04:37,222
vel ikh aykh oykhet zogn.

94
00:04:37,222 --> 00:04:39,607
mayn mame iz geven zeyer a feike.

95
00:04:40,288 --> 00:04:44,814
un, zi fleg aroysgeyn in droysn, zi fleg undz azoy

96
00:04:44,814 --> 00:04:46,461
in der kelt oystun

97
00:04:46,461 --> 00:04:50,862
un, bavashn in shney di layz mit &lt;dem alem&gt; un ibertun

98
00:04:51,156 --> 00:04:56,685
un, zi iz antlofn durkh di, s'iz dokh geven ve-...

99
00:04:57,518 --> 00:04:59,790
mir zenen dokh geven nisht in shtot

100
00:04:59,790 --> 00:05:01,944
un nisht in, tsishn bafelkerung.

101
00:05:01,944 --> 00:05:06,253
hot zi zikh ayngeshtelt dos lebn un zi iz gegangen azoy in shney.

102
00:05:06,276 --> 00:05:09,155
zi hot genemen a shmate, vos zi hot nokh gehat,

103
00:05:09,313 --> 00:05:14,597
un zi iz gegangen gebn dem goy. ven me khapt zi, derharget men zi zofort.

104
00:05:14,597 --> 00:05:18,046
nor zi, dos iz geven NELEGAL'NO.

105
00:05:18,046 --> 00:05:20,581
zi iz antlofn undz tsu rateven.

106
00:05:20,581 --> 00:05:25,355
fleg men ir gebn a por shtiklekh broyt un ales far d- far a shmate, vos mir hobn nokh gehat.

107
00:05:25,885 --> 00:05:30,688
un dos hot u- hot undz gehaltn biz, biz, dem friling.

108
00:05:31,183 --> 00:05:34,752
un friling, ikh veys nisht, s'iz geven a opmakhung.

109
00:05:35,217 --> 00:05:43,193
zey hobn gevust ale, d- ikh veys nisht ILI ANTONESCU oder mit der, mit der velt iz geven epes, m'iz, m'hot batsolt

110
00:05:43,232 --> 00:05:44,930
un m'hot undz getrofn.

111
00:05:44,953 --> 00:05:47,287
ikh veys nisht &lt;vi&gt; azoy m'hot undz getrofn,

112
00:05:47,287 --> 00:05:50,856
un vifl mentshn s'iz geven dort, fuftsn, tsvontsik mentshn,

113
00:05:50,856 --> 00:05:55,325
iz men gekumen mit a, mit tsvey vegelekh. ikh gedenk nisht merer.

114
00:05:55,433 --> 00:05:57,193
ikh hob shoyn nisht gekent geyn,

115
00:05:57,193 --> 00:06:01,923
vayl mir zenen dort dokh nisht gegangen. bin ikh gevorn f&lt;UNK&gt; mir hobn nisht gekent geyn.

116
00:06:02,436 --> 00:06:04,821
un m'hot undz gefirt keyn Bershad.

117
00:06:04,984 --> 00:06:07,863
Bershad iz geven a groys geto.

118
00:06:08,224 --> 00:06:11,407
m'hot undz arayngevorfn in a shtibele.

119
00:06:12,628 --> 00:06:16,655
dort iz geven a sakh mentshn. undz hot men gegebn aza kikhl,

120
00:06:17,185 --> 00:06:19,666
vu m'hot zikh nisht gehat afile hintsutun.

121
00:06:20,374 --> 00:06:21,315
ikh

122
00:06:21,315 --> 00:06:23,172
mit, mayn bruder,

123
00:06:23,172 --> 00:06:24,519
mit mayn mame,

124
00:06:25,048 --> 00:06:28,180
di shvester der mame's, mit tsvey zin.

125
00:06:30,195 --> 00:06:33,783
hobn mir, geven, azoy, a,

126
00:06:34,127 --> 00:06:36,382
a p- a khoydesh tsvey,

127
00:06:36,608 --> 00:06:38,846
dray. ikh ken nisht dermonen vifl.

128
00:06:39,291 --> 00:06:40,938
in der tsayt

129
00:06:41,029 --> 00:06:45,191
&lt;ho-&gt; iz vider a mol geven a opmakhung, az me zol aroysnemen di kinder

130
00:06:46,530 --> 00:06:48,802
fun, vos zenen geblibn.

131
00:06:49,872 --> 00:06:52,431
m'hot gedarft aroysforn keyn...

132
00:06:52,487 --> 00:06:54,855
in der velt. di kinder zol men rateven.

133
00:06:54,855 --> 00:06:57,240
dos iz geven batsolt

134
00:06:58,073 --> 00:07:02,674
un, un me zol d- di ki- hob i- hob ikh mit mayn bruder

135
00:07:02,747 --> 00:07:04,465
un mayn shvesterkind

136
00:07:04,465 --> 00:07:05,981
un mayn,

137
00:07:06,038 --> 00:07:07,685
ale fir kinder,

138
00:07:07,860 --> 00:07:09,541
hobn mir zikh farshribn

139
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:11,583
un m'hot undz genemen

140
00:07:11,657 --> 00:07:12,866
keyn BALTA.

141
00:07:12,923 --> 00:07:14,722
in BALTA iz geven

142
00:07:15,049 --> 00:07:16,683
a kinder-hoyz.

143
00:07:16,683 --> 00:07:17,844
nu, on eltern.

144
00:07:17,856 --> 00:07:19,331
on...

145
00:07:19,825 --> 00:07:25,556
un s'iz geven opgemakht az me vet aroysnemen di kinder un me vet rateven di kinder.

146
00:07:26,423 --> 00:07:28,341
bin ongekumen keyn BALTA

147
00:07:30,135 --> 00:07:34,567
un di mame hobn mir shoyn gelozt goysen mit, mit mayn, tante.

148
00:07:34,827 --> 00:07:40,618
zey hobn shoyn nisht gekent lebn. zey hobn shoyn nisht gehat mit, fun vos. far hunger hot men gegoyset,

149
00:07:41,374 --> 00:07:45,890
vayl, s'iz nisht geven vos tsu esn. m'hot dortn, keyner hot gornisht gegebn.

150
00:07:47,652 --> 00:07:53,021
ah, un bald hot men shoyn gedarft undz oyfheybn aroysfirn, aroys-...

151
00:07:53,021 --> 00:07:54,446
hob ikh mikh tseveynt

152
00:07:55,347 --> 00:07:56,741
far mayn bruder

153
00:07:56,899 --> 00:08:00,453
un far di &lt;kuzinen&gt;. zog ikh, "kuk,

154
00:08:00,814 --> 00:08:04,132
mir hobn ibergelozt di mame. mir veln zi keyn mol nisht zen.

155
00:08:04,594 --> 00:08:06,528
un ibergelozt di tante."

156
00:08:07,260 --> 00:08:09,920
zog ikh, "neyn. vos vet zayn mit zey...

157
00:08:10,298 --> 00:08:11,921
mir kern zikh um."

158
00:08:12,340 --> 00:08:16,468
hobn mir zikh umgekert dorf tsu dorf, vayl s'iz dokh, m'hot dokh nisht getort.

159
00:08:16,508 --> 00:08:21,902
nor azoy vi mir hobn, ikh hob ongetun a tikhl; m'hot nisht gezen ober ikh bin a yid oder nisht a yid.

160
00:08:21,942 --> 00:08:24,034
zenen mir ongekumen keyn Bershad.

161
00:08:24,405 --> 00:08:26,795
bay nakht zenen mir geshlofn in di velder,

162
00:08:26,818 --> 00:08:29,051
biz mir hobn zikh &lt;ts-&gt;,

163
00:08:29,051 --> 00:08:30,777
dos iz nisht tsu bashraybn.

164
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:33,866
kh'vel aykh dertseyln a zakh:

165
00:08:34,345 --> 00:08:37,386
az mir zenen gekumen in vald, s'iz geven a vald,

166
00:08:37,602 --> 00:08:40,313
hob ikh shoyn nisht gekent geyn. mayn bruder

167
00:08:40,419 --> 00:08:42,806
hot opgefroyrn di fis dort.

168
00:08:42,806 --> 00:08:43,920
hot er gezogt,

169
00:08:44,048 --> 00:08:46,261
"Roze, ikh ken shoyn mer nisht geyn."

170
00:08:46,512 --> 00:08:48,785
zenen mir arayngegangen in dem vald.

171
00:08:48,785 --> 00:08:50,399
kh'muz a bisl...

172
00:08:58,037 --> 00:09:02,056
un d&lt;UNK&gt;, mir zenen antshlof- er iz antshlofn gevorn un ikh oykhet.

173
00:09:02,056 --> 00:09:04,409
&lt;mir&gt; zenen geven shtark oysgemutshet.

174
00:09:06,795 --> 00:09:09,035
un er hot gezogt, er geyt nisht mer.

175
00:09:09,035 --> 00:09:10,924
di fi-, di fis trogn nisht.

176
00:09:12,229 --> 00:09:14,143
hob ikh im gez-, zenen mir

177
00:09:14,143 --> 00:09:16,949
antshlofn gevorn, kholemt zikh mir mayn tate.

178
00:09:16,949 --> 00:09:22,109
zogt er, "ir zolt zikh fun do nisht rirn, vayl bald veln geyn daytshn."

179
00:09:22,109 --> 00:09:24,412
mir zenen geven tif in vald.

180
00:09:24,412 --> 00:09:27,421
in der tsayt... ah?

181
00:09:27,421 --> 00:09:29,248
UNK

182
00:09:29,248 --> 00:09:30,639
in der tsayt,

183
00:09:30,639 --> 00:09:33,345
azoy vi ikh hob gekholemt, azoy iz gegangen daytshn

184
00:09:33,345 --> 00:09:34,158
mit di,

185
00:09:34,158 --> 00:09:37,930
mit di, fer- mit di mashinen, mit alemen.

186
00:09:37,930 --> 00:09:41,508
un mir, undz hot men nisht gezen vayl mir zenen geven in tifn vald.

187
00:09:41,508 --> 00:09:45,886
abi zey zenen avekgegangen, aldings, hobn mir zikh oyfgehoybn un gegangen vayter.

188
00:09:47,103 --> 00:09:50,907
un azoy zenen mir ongekumen keyn Bershad tsurik.

189
00:09:50,907 --> 00:09:52,734
di mame hot shoyn

190
00:09:52,734 --> 00:09:56,022
nisht gekent oyf di fis geyn un nisht,...

191
00:09:56,661 --> 00:10:00,184
dos glik, m'hot ongehoybn, m'hot, m'hot gegebn

192
00:10:00,184 --> 00:10:02,645
a, &lt;&gt;, meldung

193
00:10:03,023 --> 00:10:06,698
az me nemt, keyn arbet, keyn,

194
00:10:06,698 --> 00:10:07,792
keyn Balte.

195
00:10:08,102 --> 00:10:12,025
yidn, oyf, m-, m'hot tsunoyfgenemen, me zol zikh y-

196
00:10:12,025 --> 00:10:13,921
 yaven in a plats.

197
00:10:13,921 --> 00:10:15,929
me nemt oyf arbet keyn,

198
00:10:15,929 --> 00:10:18,660
in, in Bersh- in BALTA geto.

199
00:10:18,717 --> 00:10:24,246
UNK un m'iz in geto n- un me geyt arbetn di VALENKIs, vegn front.

200
00:10:24,589 --> 00:10:27,469
m'vet hobn a broyt mit a bisl vaser, UNK,

201
00:10:27,469 --> 00:10:30,252
azoy vi in di, m'hot gearbet, di yidn.

202
00:10:31,103 --> 00:10:35,957
hobn mir getrakht, me, vos zoln mir tun, a shtikl broyt mit a bisl vaser.

203
00:10:36,587 --> 00:10:39,773
un m'vet kenen arbetn, nor zayn farmakht tsishn...

204
00:10:39,773 --> 00:10:45,367
take m'vet undz shlogn, aldings, ober dos bisl vaser, az me zol blaybn lebn mitn shtikl broyt.

205
00:10:45,367 --> 00:10:47,704
hobn mir zikh, farshribn.

206
00:10:47,704 --> 00:10:52,646
nor ikh bin geven a kleyn kind nokh. ikh hob &lt;m-&gt;, m'hot genemen bay zekhtsn yor.

207
00:10:52,956 --> 00:10:58,414
un mayn, un di veytik iz geven groys vayl ikh bin geb- kh'hob shoyn nisht gevaksn.

208
00:10:58,525 --> 00:11:00,218
ikh bin shoyn geven

209
00:11:00,218 --> 00:11:02,652
f-, fun vu hob ikh gekent?

210
00:11:02,652 --> 00:11:04,614
hot di mame genemen a shmate

211
00:11:04,614 --> 00:11:07,288
un hot mir oysgebunen azoy vi a terk.

212
00:11:07,288 --> 00:11:12,524
di, dos tikhl azoy, a terk makhn, hekher, az ikh zol oyszen zekhtsn yor.

213
00:11:13,392 --> 00:11:18,925
un, un zi hot mikh farshtupt azoy tsishn di mentshn un ikh bin durkhgegangen.

214
00:11:18,925 --> 00:11:22,231
dem bruder hobn zey nisht gedarft, vayl der bruder iz geven,

215
00:11:22,231 --> 00:11:26,770
 demls, &lt;iz di&gt; zekhtsete yor. er iz nokh nisht geven zekhtsn, nor

216
00:11:26,770 --> 00:11:28,821
fuftsn yor, nor er iz geven hoykh.

217
00:11:28,821 --> 00:11:31,917
hot tsu im shoyn ni- keyn pasportn hot men nisht gefregt.

218
00:11:31,917 --> 00:11:33,841
keyn dok- UNK TEUDAT ZEHUT

219
00:11:33,841 --> 00:11:38,861
mir hobn nisht gedarft hobn di TEUDAT ZEHUT. m'hot zey keyner nisht gehat. keyn dokumentn iz nisht geven.

220
00:11:38,861 --> 00:11:40,683
iz geven der glik, vos...

221
00:11:40,683 --> 00:11:44,047
un azoy hobn mir zikh aroysgeratevet keyn BALTA.

222
00:11:44,273 --> 00:11:47,608
in BALTA hobn mir gearbet shtark shver.

223
00:11:47,918 --> 00:11:51,388
gegangen in shney borves. mir hobn nisht gehat vos.

224
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:53,750
di kleyder zenen geven zek.

225
00:11:54,583 --> 00:11:57,685
m'hot undz arayngetribn, azoy vi in

226
00:11:57,685 --> 00:12:03,656
a ge- s'iz geven demls OBSHCHEZHITIE. azoy heyst OBSHCHEZHITIE, &lt;&gt;?

227
00:12:03,949 --> 00:12:07,051
s'iz geven z- mit di &lt;laytsn&gt;, azoy ir hot gezen,

228
00:12:07,051 --> 00:12:09,782
di, di, di ge- lagers.

229
00:12:09,788 --> 00:12:14,996
ot dos, azoy hobn mir, in de- di mentshn vos m'hot genemen oyf der arbet...

230
00:12:15,019 --> 00:12:19,649
in geto iz geven a groyse shtub. s'hot a mol studentn geve-

231
00:12:19,649 --> 00:12:21,639
hobn zey dos farnemen far undz

232
00:12:21,639 --> 00:12:24,497
un m'hot gemakht &lt;laytses&gt; eyns oyfn andern,

233
00:12:24,503 --> 00:12:26,597
un azoy hobn mir, gelebt.

234
00:12:26,597 --> 00:12:29,505
dos glik iz geven vos mir hobn gehat a shtikl broyt

235
00:12:29,505 --> 00:12:31,754
un m'hot undz gegebn a bisl dort SUP.

236
00:12:31,945 --> 00:12:36,107
dos hobn, ho- hobn z-, hot undz geratevet biz tsun,

237
00:12:36,366 --> 00:12:39,431
biz tsun, fir un fertsikstn yor.

238
00:12:40,011 --> 00:12:43,835
fir un fertsikstn yor hot UNK, hot ongehoybn der rusisher

239
00:12:44,567 --> 00:12:48,189
zikh shlogn, er zol bafrayen di...

240
00:12:50,777 --> 00:12:52,856
iz,

241
00:12:53,528 --> 00:12:58,821
 ven m'hot ongehoybn bafrayen, dos iz, B-, BALTA hot men bafrayt,

242
00:12:59,603 --> 00:13:02,383
 hot men befray- bafrayt...

243
00:13:02,573 --> 00:13:04,676
dem bruder hot men derharget

244
00:13:04,699 --> 00:13:06,105
dray teg

245
00:13:06,105 --> 00:13:07,235
in IYAR.

246
00:13:07,235 --> 00:13:08,405
IYAR,

247
00:13:09,070 --> 00:13:11,882
der yidisher khoydesh, vayl ikh, ge-

248
00:13:12,192 --> 00:13:13,384
IYAR.

249
00:13:13,761 --> 00:13:17,981
dos iz, far, far pu- purim-peysekh. &lt;IYAR&gt;.

250
00:13:19,701 --> 00:13:21,770
un dray teg befor

251
00:13:22,755 --> 00:13:27,503
m'hot, derharget dem bruder, nokh dray teg iz arayn, hot men undz bafrayt.

252
00:13:27,279 --> 00:13:28,661
ver hot im derharget?

253
00:13:27,503 --> 00:13:27,997
&lt;z-&gt;

254
00:13:28,527 --> 00:13:30,643
di daytshn, di esesovtses

255
00:13:30,643 --> 00:13:33,847
zenen arayngekumen &lt;d-&gt;... s'iz nisht nor bay undz in shtub.

256
00:13:33,893 --> 00:13:37,387
dos hot men aroysgenemen... ir zent dokh geven in der, in dem o...

257
00:13:37,387 --> 00:13:40,840
s'ershte hobn zey gegreykht tsu undz. m'hot aroysgenemen m- a-,

258
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,730
m'hot aroysgenemen fun der shtub...

259
00:13:42,730 --> 00:13:44,467
zenen nor geblibn tsen mener,

260
00:13:44,507 --> 00:13:47,589
&lt;nor meynstns iz&gt; geven kinder mit, mit froyen.

261
00:13:47,967 --> 00:13:51,116
fun di tsen mener iz geven mayn bruder un mayn kuzin.

262
00:13:51,898 --> 00:13:53,114
ikh gedenk

263
00:13:53,114 --> 00:13:54,525
nokh tsvey mentshn:

264
00:13:55,527 --> 00:13:58,544
familye Vays, vos m'hot im geshosn.

265
00:13:58,544 --> 00:14:01,809
er hot zikh aropgev- er hot zikh aropge-

266
00:14:01,809 --> 00:14:05,893
un di K- di, KADUR- di, PULIs, di...

267
00:14:05,893 --> 00:14:07,316
zenen geblibn in im.

268
00:14:07,575 --> 00:14:08,868
un eyner

269
00:14:08,976 --> 00:14:10,758
iz gelofn, iz arayn,

270
00:14:10,832 --> 00:14:14,144
Shoy- Shoykhet, a bavuster,

271
00:14:14,144 --> 00:14:17,879
gevir fun &lt;Bend&gt;, vos er iz geven mit undz. iz arayn in &lt;Drubone&gt;.

272
00:14:18,088 --> 00:14:20,346
nokh dem hot er bakumen a,

273
00:14:20,346 --> 00:14:23,718
a in- a infektsye oyf di fis, m'hot im opgeshnitn.

274
00:14:23,995 --> 00:14:25,879
un &lt;dos&gt;, di ershte,

275
00:14:25,952 --> 00:14:30,648
 ven der daytsh iz gekumen, hot gezogt, ar- aroysnemen di, di kinder,

276
00:14:30,648 --> 00:14:31,717
di mener,

277
00:14:32,314 --> 00:14:34,032
hot mayn mame im bahaltn.

278
00:14:34,032 --> 00:14:37,045
zi hot zikh aroyfgeleygt oyf im. zi hot aroyfgeleygt a,

279
00:14:37,045 --> 00:14:40,094
a koldre, a, a iberbet hobn mir nokh gehat,

280
00:14:40,094 --> 00:14:42,443
vos mir hobn zi geshlept dem gantsn veg.

281
00:14:42,443 --> 00:14:45,487
un UNK, un zi hot zikh aroyfgeleygt un ikh hob mikh aroyfgeleygt.

282
00:14:45,679 --> 00:14:50,485
un ven der esesovets hot gezogt, "ale d- ale yidn aroys, ale mener,

283
00:14:50,485 --> 00:14:52,940
un tomer nisht, vet zayn shlekht,"

284
00:14:52,940 --> 00:14:53,960
hot er &lt;t-&gt;

285
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:57,913
iz geshtanen, der daytsh hot gezen, se tsitert epes unter der,

286
00:14:57,913 --> 00:14:59,865
unter der, iberbet.

287
00:15:00,428 --> 00:15:03,442
hot er, iz er aleyn aroys. zogt er, "dos bin ikh."

288
00:15:03,955 --> 00:15:10,173
un der shvesterkind un dortn di tsen mentshn fun undzer, hot men aroysgenemen.

289
00:15:10,452 --> 00:15:12,431
bin ikh nokhgelofn, vayl,

290
00:15:12,431 --> 00:15:14,191
bin nokhgelofn nokh im.

291
00:15:15,075 --> 00:15:20,216
un, v- un im hot men aroysgenemen oyf, in hoyf, in a groysn hoyf.

292
00:15:21,859 --> 00:15:28,755
ven er hot geshosn, hob ikh mikh aropgevorfn. &lt;, d-&gt; s'ershte vos kh'hob mikh aroy- vos ikh hob mir genemen in kop:

293
00:15:28,755 --> 00:15:31,286
vos &lt;s'vet&gt; nisht zayn, zol ikh mikh varfn oyf dr'erd.

294
00:15:31,815 --> 00:15:34,121
ven m'hot mikh s'ershte mol geshlogn,

295
00:15:34,498 --> 00:15:35,842
fun dem gold,

296
00:15:36,372 --> 00:15:41,884
hob ikh mikh, tseleygt un &lt;zol&gt; meynen az shoyn, s'iz, ikh bin, er zol mikh mer nit shlogn.

297
00:15:41,940 --> 00:15:43,891
un do hob ikh gevust az ikh...

298
00:15:44,185 --> 00:15:48,333
er hot gesh-, ikh hob mikh zofort aropgevorfn oyf dr'erd. er hot geshosn,

299
00:15:48,333 --> 00:15:50,181
zey hobn shoyn nisht gehat keyn tsayt.

300
00:15:50,181 --> 00:15:52,349
zey hobn oysgeshosn di,

301
00:15:52,349 --> 00:15:53,976
di ershte &lt;g-&gt;...

302
00:15:54,023 --> 00:15:57,949
ikh mit mayne oygn hob gezen vi m'hot geshosn di mentshn,

303
00:15:58,680 --> 00:16:02,448
un di ershte &lt;ge-&gt; PULIs, di ershte KADURIM

304
00:16:02,448 --> 00:16:04,102
iz arayn in mayn bruder

305
00:16:04,102 --> 00:16:05,998
un s'hot opgerisn a halbn kop.

306
00:16:06,021 --> 00:16:10,048
der halb-, mit di gehirn iz avek a halbn meter, nokh mer.

307
00:16:11,826 --> 00:16:13,154
&lt;un&gt; ikh hob gevart

308
00:16:13,154 --> 00:16:16,133
az zey zoln avekgeyn, di daytshn. m'hot nisht getort.

309
00:16:16,133 --> 00:16:17,607
in tsveytn tog

310
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:21,273
hob ikh aroysgek- &lt;u- u- un da-&gt; hot er zikh umgekert,

311
00:16:21,580 --> 00:16:26,603
un er hot gevolt, er hot shoyn nisht gehat keyn tsayt undz tsu shisn, vayl er hot gedarft yedn oysshisn.

312
00:16:26,895 --> 00:16:28,779
hot er genemen a granate

313
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:30,925
un er hot arayngevorfn... iz geven

314
00:16:30,925 --> 00:16:32,036
di tir,

315
00:16:32,262 --> 00:16:36,542
&lt;vo-&gt;, akegn dem fentster, un di granate iz aroys,

316
00:16:36,733 --> 00:16:40,724
un, un a nes, s'iz aroys oyf der gas un mir zenen geblibn lebn.

317
00:16:43,753 --> 00:16:48,100
 tsishn di iz do a sakh mentshn vos ikh ken, vos zenen geblibn lebn,

318
00:16:48,546 --> 00:16:50,379
zenen do, lebn haynt,

319
00:16:51,533 --> 00:16:54,362
vos zey zenen geblibn lebn. nisht a sakh,

320
00:16:54,368 --> 00:16:58,723
nor s'iz nokh do mentshn vos zenen geblibn lebn.

321
00:16:59,920 --> 00:17:05,027
un az, in tsveytn tog bin ikh aroysgegangen, az mayn mame zol nisht zen

322
00:17:05,521 --> 00:17:07,598
dem groysn umglik, dem kop,

323
00:17:07,598 --> 00:17:09,560
a- er iz nishto &lt;in halbn&gt;.

324
00:17:09,560 --> 00:17:11,253
hob ikh genemen a tikhl,

325
00:17:11,444 --> 00:17:14,138
ikh hob tsunoyfgenemen di gehirn mitn kop,

326
00:17:14,365 --> 00:17:16,062
ikh hob im ayn-....

327
00:17:16,930 --> 00:17:21,417
un di mame hot geshrign, gevolt ikh zol im araynnemen; er vet vern farfroyrn.

328
00:17:23,055 --> 00:17:25,597
kh'hob im gemuzt araynnemen. ikh hob gebetn mentshn.

329
00:17:25,637 --> 00:17:27,166
zi vil im onvaremen.

330
00:17:27,375 --> 00:17:30,426
nokh dem, ven di rusishe zenen shoyn arayngekumen,

331
00:17:30,426 --> 00:17:32,499
dos iz shoyn geven nokh dray teg.

332
00:17:33,045 --> 00:17:35,078
rusishe zenen arayngekumen,

333
00:17:36,866 --> 00:17:38,370
hot ongehoybn

334
00:17:38,370 --> 00:17:39,603
bombardirn.

335
00:17:40,690 --> 00:17:43,738
s'iz nokh nisht geven, s'iz nokh geven milkhome.

336
00:17:44,470 --> 00:17:46,421
ven ikh, m'hot aroysgetrogn...

337
00:17:46,849 --> 00:17:49,981
mir hobn aleyn im, bagrobn.

338
00:17:50,258 --> 00:17:51,689
mir hobn im aleyn.

339
00:17:51,689 --> 00:17:53,964
nokh dray teg iz shoyn geven di rusishe.

340
00:17:54,190 --> 00:17:57,626
hobn mir im genemen mit a leyter. vos hobn mir gekent tun?

341
00:17:58,003 --> 00:18:00,663
un ven mir hobn nor aroysgetrogn im

342
00:18:00,687 --> 00:18:02,014
oyf der leyter,

343
00:18:02,830 --> 00:18:09,610
&lt;ho-&gt; iz ongelofn di, di, &lt;,&gt; AVIRONIM, un s'iz gevorn a bom- bom- m-...

344
00:18:09,610 --> 00:18:11,368
dos iz geven,

345
00:18:11,368 --> 00:18:13,133
s'iz nisht tsu dertseyln &lt;aykh&gt;.

346
00:18:13,242 --> 00:18:14,993
nor mir hobn im bagrobn.

347
00:18:14,993 --> 00:18:17,482
mir hobn dem kuzin oykh bagrobn in eynem.

348
00:18:17,482 --> 00:18:19,175
mir hobn gemakht a,

349
00:18:19,823 --> 00:18:22,255
a, beyde lign zey in eyn grub.

350
00:18:22,708 --> 00:18:24,063
oyfn yidishn,

351
00:18:24,063 --> 00:18:26,924
azoy vi mir zenen yidishe kinder, hobn mir gevolt

352
00:18:26,924 --> 00:18:30,380
az zey zoln vern bagrobn oyfn

353
00:18:30,123 --> 00:18:32,028
yidishn besoylem.

354
00:18:31,146 --> 00:18:33,789
yidishn besoylem, vu zey lign haynt.

355
00:18:34,588 --> 00:18:36,776
s'iz &lt;dur-&gt;, mir hobn gezen

356
00:18:36,782 --> 00:18:39,189
az mir hobn nisht, &lt;un vos zoln mir&gt; tun do?

357
00:18:39,853 --> 00:18:43,216
hobn mir zikh tsunoyfgenemen etlekhe mentshn:

358
00:18:43,216 --> 00:18:46,833
ikh mit mayn, b- b- mit mayn mame,

359
00:18:47,042 --> 00:18:50,228
i- di tante mit ir kuzi- mit mayn kuzin,

360
00:18:50,228 --> 00:18:52,543
un nokh mentshn vos zenen gegangen, vos zenen nokh,

361
00:18:52,543 --> 00:18:56,026
nokh do di kinder fun zey, nokh &lt;a&gt; por mentshn vos zenen do.

362
00:18:56,026 --> 00:18:59,827
m'iz aroysgegangen dem ershtn may...dos vel ikh keyn mol nisht fargesn...

363
00:19:00,171 --> 00:19:01,380
tsu fus,

364
00:19:01,875 --> 00:19:03,502
dorf tsu dorf,

365
00:19:03,502 --> 00:19:09,058
shtetl tsu shtetl. &lt;vif- v-&gt; vu s'iz geven der front, vu &lt;d-&gt; s'iz geven der...

366
00:19:09,385 --> 00:19:11,618
hobn mir zikh opgeshtelt biz me nemt.

367
00:19:11,618 --> 00:19:14,694
mir hobn dokh nisht gekent, keyn Tshernovits hobn mir &lt;nokh&gt; nisht gekent geyn.

368
00:19:14,694 --> 00:19:16,807
Keshenev iz nokh nisht geven opgenumen.

369
00:19:16,807 --> 00:19:19,439
&lt;zenen&gt; mir gevoynt a bisl UNK in Belts.

370
00:19:19,439 --> 00:19:21,894
s'iz geven leydike shtiber, flegn mir arayngeyn.

371
00:19:21,894 --> 00:19:24,774
do hobn mir shoyn nisht moyre gehat, do zenen mir tsugegangen tsum feld.

372
00:19:24,774 --> 00:19:27,477
mir hobn genemen a shtikl, b-

373
00:19:27,477 --> 00:19:30,880
vos s'iz geven oyfn feld, zise burikes, dos...

374
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:35,494
di goyim hobn a bisl gegebn. dos iz shoyn nisht geven...

375
00:19:35,494 --> 00:19:37,885
nor mir zenen gegangen tomed hintern front.

376
00:19:37,885 --> 00:19:42,801
vu m'hot opgenemen, dort, zenen mir, zenen mir gegangen, biz keyn Tshernovits.

377
00:19:42,814 --> 00:19:44,313
in Tshernovits

378
00:19:44,313 --> 00:19:46,200
zenen mir ongekumen...

379
00:19:46,932 --> 00:19:50,472
ikh ken nisht ge- gedenken vifl es hot gedoyert der veg,

380
00:19:50,472 --> 00:19:52,174
nor s'hot gedoyert a sakh,

381
00:19:52,483 --> 00:19:53,889
vayl,

382
00:19:53,889 --> 00:19:56,176
 s'iz nokh nisht &lt;Keshe-&gt; mir hobn gedarft geyn

383
00:19:56,176 --> 00:19:58,690
durkh Belts, durkh Keshenev, UNK hobn mir...

384
00:19:58,690 --> 00:20:02,617
iz umedum iz geven di b- hobn mir d- zenen mir geven hinter der,

385
00:20:02,617 --> 00:20:04,847
dort hot men bombardirt, dort hot men geshlogn,

386
00:20:04,847 --> 00:20:06,891
nor mir hobn nisht gehat keyn andern veg. me hot,

387
00:20:06,891 --> 00:20:09,489
m'iz gegangen. vos hot men gehat tsu trakhtn?

388
00:20:09,489 --> 00:20:11,727
mir hobn shoyn nisht getrakht fun undzer lebn. az me,

389
00:20:11,727 --> 00:20:13,122
mir hobn gezen a shtub,

390
00:20:13,122 --> 00:20:14,398
zenen mir arayngegangen.

391
00:20:14,792 --> 00:20:16,828
mir hobn zikh avekge-

392
00:20:17,020 --> 00:20:20,375
 m'iz gegangen betn a shtikl broyt bay di goyim.

393
00:20:20,375 --> 00:20:22,692
m- s'i- mir hobn shoyn UNK.

394
00:20:22,692 --> 00:20:24,281
dos iz geven undzer lebn.

395
00:20:24,281 --> 00:20:25,569
un nokh dem,

396
00:20:25,828 --> 00:20:29,462
bin ongekumen keyn Tshernovits, hot men undz nisht arayngelozt keyn Tshernovits.

397
00:20:29,462 --> 00:20:31,538
m'hot gegebn a bafel

398
00:20:31,538 --> 00:20:33,450
az mir zenen farlayzikt

399
00:20:33,743 --> 00:20:35,068
un mit krank.

400
00:20:35,068 --> 00:20:37,365
hot men undz nisht arayngelozt in Tshernovits.

401
00:20:37,894 --> 00:20:39,643
hot men undz opgehaltn

402
00:20:40,020 --> 00:20:41,229
bay der brik.

403
00:20:41,944 --> 00:20:45,222
&lt;nu&gt;, di, &lt;min-&gt; in, mit, zek, &lt;kl- &gt;

404
00:20:45,222 --> 00:20:50,156
UNK, far, m'hot undz gegebn a kuk on, hot men undz nisht. nor mir kinder, ikh mit mayn kuzin,

405
00:20:50,803 --> 00:20:55,353
s- mayn tante... s'iz geven a tante mayne, vos zi hot zikh gefunen in geto;

406
00:20:55,444 --> 00:20:57,348
ir man iz geven

407
00:20:57,348 --> 00:20:58,796
a spetsyalist

408
00:20:59,055 --> 00:21:00,300
inzhenyer,

409
00:21:00,300 --> 00:21:01,829
un ir eydem oykh.

410
00:21:01,829 --> 00:21:05,186
hot men im gel- iz er geblibn in geto, un er hot gearbet;

411
00:21:05,186 --> 00:21:09,022
zey hobn gedarft im hobn. hot er gearbet, nor er iz geven in geto.

